verbose_text: Regarding fatty acid oxidation, the enzymes acyl-CoA synthetase I (ACSL1), long-chain acyl CoA dehydrogenase (ACADL), and enoyl-CoA hydratase/3-hydroxyacyl-CoA (EHHADH) have also been shown to be regulated by acetylation and present altered acetylation in clock deficient mice.
evidence: acetylation and present altered acetylation in clock
